commit.message: Rename to sendxmpp.sc, scalafmt, bump Smack to 4.4.6
Do not use fully-qualified name to reference class
Add documentation to command and parameter
Construct message outside of the try/catch block
Provide a proper error message if no credentials file is found
Add TODO note that BC provider code an be removed later
Ensure connection will be disconnected via try/catch block

Remove the BC provider
